{"type": "article", "id": 23589, "title": "英国封面设计学院奖新鲜出炉，瞧瞧这些好看的书", "description": "作为老牌出版大国，英国的书籍设计还是辣么美。", "date": "2016-03-10T07:00:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 24664, "name": "书籍封面设计"}, {"id": 24665, "name": "Jamie Keenan"}, {"id": 24666, "name": "Jon Gary"}], "category": 17, "author": 103970, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 209, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702105904hfH4QU5xEz7ucJKp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>从 2014 年开始，书籍封面设计师 Jon Gary 和 Jamie Keenan 开始举办英国封面设计学院奖（The Academy of British Cover Design，简称 ABCD），用以表彰优秀的英国书籍设计师。也包括电子书。 </p>\n<p><a href=\"www.keenandesign.com\">Jamie Keenan </a>是业内著名的设计师，他经手了卡夫卡、纳博科夫、艾略特、道金斯等著名的文学作品。<a href=\"http://gray318.com/\">Jon Gary </a>则是行业经历 12 年的自由设计师，曾经设计了 J.K. 罗琳《偶发空缺》。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105859UF9osmhkSG2c5TVR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Jamie 设计的《洛丽塔》</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>他俩曾提出关于<a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/booksblog/2012/aug/16/book-cover-theories-edinburgh-festival\">书籍封面设计的 20 条理论</a>，教你如何按照这些有迹可循的规则设计出好看的封面：比如第 18 条“狗屎理论”，再难看、平庸的图案当你换着色号把它做成系列书籍的封面，都有可能得一个什么设计奖。 </p>\n<p>ABCD 的奖项分成 10 个类别：儿童、青春、科幻／幻想、大众、文学、犯罪／惊悚、系列设计、经典／再发行、女性小说、非虚构类。来看看<a href=\"http://abcoverd.co.uk/\">今年的获奖作品</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b> 儿童</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105859GgKF09waqZUv4fQn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40293638\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Designed by Coralie Bickford-Smith</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>青春</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105900zHVp4R8KUv25iaOS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.52352941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Designed by Kate Gaughran</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>科幻／幻想</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105900q91vyXu0nBixtMgD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.59411765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Designed by Ben Summers</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>大众</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105901vKRZfrQtGe82CJ6u.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.61176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Designed by Joanna Thomson Illustrated by Maricor/Maricar</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>犯罪／惊悚</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105901H91tloEbe8xGvZPj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5369863\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Designed by Richard Bravery</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>非虚构类</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105902JuZrlC6DjB1xgeIY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.30280374\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">The Very Best Recipes Inspired by the Simple Egg by Blanche Vaughan，Designed by Richard Bravery</figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>系列设计</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021059023WPOlt0bq4LfQzUB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Art Directed by James Jones Illustrated by Pietari Posti</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>经典／再发行</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105902iKoyTD5BNrVRUGLj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50546448\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Designed by Sinem Erkas</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>女性小说</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105903mEJzNFoWldKCTRMO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.51176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://abcoverd.co.uk/\">点击查看所有入围作品</a></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://abcoverd.co.uk/2015/index.html\">2015 年获奖作品</a></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://abcoverd.co.uk/2014/index.html\">2014 年获奖作品</a></p>\n\n"}